snippet.title: Iron Saga VS - Launch and Roadmap Trailer
snippet.description:
- Official Website: https://en.ironsagavs.com/
- Steam store page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2463800/Iron_Saga_VS/ 
- Official Discord server: https://discord.gg/xuXfR6e44C 

Iron Saga VS launches for PC on Steam! 
Fight alongside your favorite classic anime Mecha and Iron Saga's own powerful original units.

12 powerful mecha with 2 unique arsenals each, multiple beautifully animated Supermoves and quick-loading rollback online play!

It is finally time to get in the robot - Round 1! ENGAGE! 

#IronSagaVS #fightinggames #animegames #gaming #mecha
